Millions of messages per second
Automatic load balancing

14. How do you monitor Pub/Sub?
Answer: Monitor: Backlog size , Unacknowledged messages , Publish rate , Delivery latency  , Subscriber throughput
Using: Cloud Monitoring and Cloud Logging

